WEBVTT

00:00:00.339 --> 00:00:18.026
Good morning, family. I have a word for you today—some things the Lord has been showing me in prayer—and I'm just going to get right to it. I was asking the Lord if He had anything for the people.

00:00:18.027 --> 00:00:36.604
I haven't given a fresh word like this for a while, and while asking Him for direction for this channel, He said, 'Make prayer a staple.'He keeps telling me to make prayer on this channel a staple; that's the go-to.

00:00:36.605 --> 00:00:42.390
Always teach the people to pray and teach them to jump in the rivers.

00:00:42.391 --> 00:00:49.874
It's priority number one, and I haven't been faithful enough with doing that, but I'm going to do it more and more.

00:00:49.875 --> 00:01:16.891
