00:01:16.892 --> 00:01:30.428
How many different ones do we hear? Who's right? You do this because you're not hearing Him for yourself—I'm just trying to be real with you—you're not seeking Him and finding Him.

00:01:30.429 --> 00:01:37.952
You go to the nearest YouTube channel to see who has the word for the day, and a lot of you are being led astray.

00:01:37.953 --> 00:01:45.218
You have got to get in the Word, make it a priority in your life, and have a relationship with the Lord yourself.

00:01:45.219 --> 00:02:06.211
He will talk to you on a day-to-day basis. Listen to Him through His Word; put it on audio through the player—that is God speaking to you.

00:02:06.212 --> 00:02:11.548
It's priority number one: get in the Word and make it a foundation in your life.

00:02:11.549 --> 00:02:25.726
Stop going around looking for Prophet Susie and Prophet Billy Bob, and then forgetting the true prophetic words.

00:02:25.727 --> 00:02:29.949
They're not getting it down inside of them; they're not meditating on that prophetic word.

00:02:29.950 --> 00:02:37.472
